
label s178:
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    play music 'sound/01.mp3'
    
    "The hand of the clock ticks by."
    
    "It's been two hours since we came here."
    
    "\"----Phew.\""
    
    "I've started to settle down and there's nobody around now."
    
    "The night starts to deepen."
    
    "\"Arcueid, is it alright now?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Yeah, it's alright.\""
    
    "She agrees with me, but she doesn't really seem enthused yet."
    
    "\"You've been acting strange since before, Arcueid."
    
    "Is there something wrong?\""
    
    "\"----Not really."
    
    "I was just concerned about that bandaged man you told me about.\""
    
    "Arcueid sighs as she ponders to herself."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T08.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Oh, that's right."
    
    "Shiki, last night someone hit on me here.\""
    
    "\"----Huh?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T11.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"I'm saying, some guy started to talk to me here.\""
    
    "\".... No, I heard you."
    
    "I thought you said you were thinking about that bandaged man though.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"I was, that's why I remembered."
    
    "Just like when you were attacked, someone started to talk to me.\""
    
    "\".... I see."
    
    "Well, that's good."
    
    "Just looking from the outside, you are a beautiful person so if you were waiting around by yourself, it is entirely natural for a guy to talk to you.\""
    
    "I give a serious response."
    
    "Sometimes, I'm a little too honest."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"You think so?"
    
    "I thought it was an enemy at first, but I remembered you saying something before about how I always stand out."
    
    "So after studying him briefly, I saw he was just a human.\""
    
    "\".... Wait a minute."
    
    "Don't tell me you did something to the guy trying to hit on you?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T14.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"No, I didn't do anything."
    
    "I just talked with him a little bit and made him forget about it."
    
    ".... But if I didn't remember what you said, I might have.\""
    
    "\"I see."
    
    "Good job, Arcueid."
    
    "I guess even you can make distinctions.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Of course."
    
    "It would have to take someone like you to make me angry.\""
    
    "She seems to say this with some amusement."
    
    ".... Well, it's natural for someone to get mad if they were killed."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "I sigh as I glance around the park."
    
    ".... A month ago."
    
    "If those serial murders never started occurring, there would still be young couples around and the figures of students hanging out."
    
    "But now, the only ones talking here are me and Arcueid."
    
    "I calmly think about my current situation."
    
    "Since when did Tohno Shiki step off onto the path of such a world----?"
    
    stop music
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T08.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Ah."
    
    "Hey, see.\""
    
    "Arcueid suddenly calls out to me."
    
    "\"What, did something happen?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T09.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Yeah."
    
    "See?"
    
    "Look at the clock."
    
    "It's time.\""
    
    "She points to the park's clock while giving a full smile."
    
    "Looking----it's ten o'clock now."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    play music 'sound/08.mp3'
    
    "The promised time."
    
    "The promise backed only by words, to meet here at ten o'clock at night."
    
    ".... Last night."
    
    "The promised time I couldn't keep."
    
    "\"--------\""
    
    "My words get stuck in my throat."
    
    "Why does such a trivial thing suddenly cause my chest to tighten?"
    
    "Why.. does such a trivial thing make her so happy?"
    
    ".... I really don't understand."
    
    "I spent all day with her today."
    
    "But it never felt like she was really a vampire."
    
    "\".... Let me ask you something.\""
    
    "----Stop it, Shiki."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T09.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Yeah, what is it?\""
    
    "\".... Are you..\""
    
    "----Don't ask her that."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Um, am I what?\""
    
    "\".... Really a vampire?\""
    
    "----What kind of answer are you hoping for?"
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T12.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"A vampire?--what's with that all of a sudden, Shiki?\""
    
    "\"It's not all of a sudden."
    
    "I was just thinking.\""
    
    "I look away."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T11.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Huh?"
    
    "I can't tell if you're really stubborn or not."
    
    "I don't really mind, but that's pretty insulting."
    
    "Tell me why you're asking that.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "There's no reason."
    
    "But----at the same time, there's no real proof she's a vampire either."
    
    "So----"
    
    "\".... Well, you said you don't even like to see blood."
    
    "What kind of vampire is that?"
    
    "You even said you weren't a full vampire, but a vampire that hasn't sucked blood isn't a vampire, is it?\""
    
    "----That's not it."
    
    "Isn't it just that Tohno Shiki, deep inside, wishes she wasn't a vampire?"
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T06.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Shiki."
    
    "Stand up.\""
    
    "Arcueid approaches the park bench."
    
    "I stand up."
    
    "\"----\""
    
    "Our eyes meet."
    
    "We're about two meters apart."
    
    "Arcueid gives a huge sigh, and suddenly grins."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T08.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"I guess you're right."
    
    "I even thought about it myself."
    
    "I wondered, is Arcueid Brunestud really a vampire?"
    
    "Ahaha,\" she laughs."
    
    ".... That's a relief."
    
    "I thought this question would insult her----but thankfully, she seems to have taken it as a joke."
    
    "\"----Yeah."
    
    "You really don't look like a vampire at all.\""
    
    "\"Ahaha,\" Arcueid laughs again."
    
    "\"Then, shall we try?\""
    
    "She says this, still smiling."
    
    "\"Try----eh?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Shall we see if I can really drink blood?"
    
    "If I could, can you give me a prize, Shiki?\""
    
    "\"Wha----\""
    
    "With that smile still on her face, she takes a step closer."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    stop music
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_02.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Tap, tap."
    
    "Her footsteps echo in the air."
    
    "I know she's joking."
    
    "Still----I can't move, at all."
    
    "\"Wa----\""
    
    "--it."
    
    "But I can't even finish."
    
    "It's not her power----but me who stops."
    
    "Closer."
    
    "One step."
    
    "Another step."
    
    "Looking down, bit by bit."
    
    "I----not even able to lift a single finger, am transfixed by her lips----"
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\"Shiki, you said I wasn't a full vampire, but....\""
    
    "A sweet voice that seems to echo in the back of my head."
    
    "Another step, and the footsteps stop."
    
    "---You know, drinking blood is very easy."
    
    "I hear that voice right by my ear."
    
    scene expression 'background/event/ARK_E05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Her body weight presses up against me."
    
    "\"------\""
    
    "My throat freezes and I can't even speak."
    
    "I can only feel her breath on my neck."
    
    "----It's hot like a burning fire."
    
    "\"Ar-----\""
    
    "I stop calling her name."
    
    "With my own will, I stop."
    
    "Because I know if I call out her name, she'll pull away."
    
    "\"------\""
    
    "Her breath is so close."
    
    "Her white fingers on my shoulders are trembling."
    
    "----She's, scared."
    
    "My mind is blank and I'm not scared at all."
    
    "But, Arcueid is the only one shaking."
    
    "I can't see her face."
    
    "Just the swirling of her breath around my neck, and the feel of her trembling body against mine."
    
    "It changes from a weak breeze to heavy breathing."
    
    "\"Ar---cueid?\""
    
    "\"It was------supposed to be a joke.\""
    
    "Her voice shakes."
    
    "The fingers on my shoulder cease their trembling."
    
    "Instead----they dig into my shoulders like a bird's talons."
    
    "\"Gah-----!\""
    
    "A pained gasp escapes me."
    
    "But her claws do not let up."
    
    "They sink in as if not allowing me to escape."
    
    "\"Arc----I'm sorry, I guess I joked around too much."
    
    "I'm sorry----so can you, let go?\""
    
    "\"Shi----ki.\""
    
    "Her fingers don't move."
    
    "----This isn't good."
    
    "My mind screams in warning and I gather up all my strength."
    
    "My arms move to push her away."
    
    "Before that,"
    
    "Pain shoots through my shoulders."
    
    "\"............!!!\""
    
    "My arms can't move at all."
    
    "Her vice-like grip on my shoulders cause my arms to go numb."
    
    "\"----,----,--------\""
    
    ".... I can feel her breath grow even wilder against my neck."
    
    "Maddening."
    
    "Her teeth almost touch my neck."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_11.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\"N----No....!\""
    
    "After the grip increases one more time from her white fingers,"
    
    "Arcueid flies back, practically screaming."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    play music 'sound/09.mp3'
    
    "Panting fills the air."
    
    "Hard breathing echoes through the park."
    
    "My ragged breathing-----Arcueid's trembling breaths."
    
    "\"Shi------ki.\""
    
    "Her entire body shaking, she gasps as if to suck in the entire atmosphere as she stares in disbelief at her two hands."
    
    "Her white fingertips are now dripping with my blood."
    
    "The redness flows from her fingers to her palms, and then along her arms."
    
    "\"Ah----\""
    
    "She looks at it, and seems to be on the verge of collapse."
    
    "\".... Arcueid, just now, was----\""
    
    "I call out to her."
    
    "Looking up from the blood on her hands, she meets my gaze."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T18.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Shi----ki?\""
    
    "\".... Yeah, I'm here."
    
    "Just now, was----a joke, but it seems like it went a little far.\""
    
    "I say that, wanting to let this end just as a joke."
    
    "But I guess it didn't work out."
    
    "\"Shiki----I, just----\""
    
    "Her eyes lose sanity."
    
    "\"Got----very thirsty----\""
    
    "Her convulsions become deeper, and even now----she seems like she'll crumble to the ground."
    
    "\"Please----go home, Shiki.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_28B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\"Hey, Arcueid....!?\""
    
    "With that, she starts to run."
    
    "She disappears fast."
    
    "Not like she ran before, where she was taking me into account."
    
    "With a speed I couldn't even match if I sprinted with all my strength, she vanishes into the night towards the city."
    
    "\"----Wha..\""
    
    "She thinks I can just go back after seeing her like that?"
    
    "\"That idiot----where is she going when she's in that much pain....!?\""
    
    "I can't just go back home."
    
    "Even though I don't know where to find her, I start to run after her into town."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    stop music
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_25B.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "----I don't see her anywhere."
    
    "The city is too big, and it's nearly impossible for a single person to track her down when she leaves no trace behind."
    
    "I'd be much more likely to find her if I predict where she's going to go rather than blindly searching."
    
    "Then----"
    
    menu:
        
        "Go to Arcueid's apartment.":
            
            $ selected = 1
        
        'Look in the commercial district.':
            
            $ selected = 2
        
        'The school, perhaps?':
            
            $ selected = 3
    
    if selected == 1:
        
        jump s179
    
    if selected == 2:
        
        jump s180
    
    if selected == 3:
        
        jump s500
